title: “Joe Biden is President.”
description: Joe Biden is sworn in as the 46th President of the United States, Kamala Harris is sworn in as the 49th Vice President, former game show host Donald Trump retires to Florida, and the new administration immediately gets to work.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
